overview: September 18th, 2011 :: In 12 Large: Summit round-robin action, Ophidian tries to defeat Sara Del Rey and Eddie Kingston tries to keep his lead when he takes on Fire Ant! Sinn Bodhi and The Batiri battle The Spectral Envoy! In the main event, Mike Quackenbush and Jigsaw defend los Campeonatos de Parejas against the challenge of F.I.S.T.!
title: Chikara Martyr Yourself To Caution
